data.description: Opportunity is knocking! This is your chance to own a slice of heaven with so many features I can't type them all, including vinyl plank flooring and smart home features. This home is located within close proximity to an abundance of shopping and dining. Minutes to DFW Airport. Storage galore with 6 closets! Plenty of room for play or entertaining in the large backyard. Owner's suite features separate shower and soaking tub, and dual sink vanity. Community features include a large pool and playground. Buyer to verify all measurements and schools.
